text: "Baby Jane" is a 1983 song by Rod Stewart. It is from his 12th studio album Body Wishes. It topped the single charts in the United Kingdom, South Africa, Spain, Ireland, Germany and Belgium. It was his last UK number 1 single to date. It also reached the top 10 in Australia, Austria, France, the Netherlands, Norway, Sweden and Switzerland. ==References== Category:1983 songs Category:Rod Stewart songs
